      <h2>Ergonomic back-support seating &mdash; paired with BBI&rsquo;s broader institutional catalog.</h2>
      <div class="lp-intro__body">
        <p>ObusForme is a consumer-recognizable ergonomic seating brand specializing in back-support and lumbar-focused task chairs. Distributed within the Global Furniture Group family. Best known to buyers for ergonomic-care models that come up by name in procurement &mdash; the 1240-3 in particular is widely specified for institutional ergonomic seating.</p>
        <p>ObusForme&rsquo;s specialized seating is a strong fit when a buyer wants brand-recognized ergonomic support. For workspaces that need broader product depth &mdash; desks, tables, storage, additional seating brands &mdash; Brant Business Interiors pairs ObusForme with the wider institutional catalog and handles design layout, Ontario install, and OECM-compliant procurement.</p>
