        </article>
        <article class="lp-diff-card">
          <span class="lp-diff-card__num">By name</span>
          <h3 class="lp-diff-card__label">Consumer-recognizable</h3>
          <p class="lp-diff-card__sentence">Unlike many specialist brands, ObusForme is widely known to end users. Procurement teams hear the brand name from staff and incumbents; BBI keeps it available alongside the broader institutional catalog.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="lp-diff-card">
          <span class="lp-diff-card__num">GFG family</span>
